name: J-League Eleven Beat 1997
description: J-League Eleven Beat 1997 (Jリーグサッカーイレブンビート1997) is a soccer game for the Nintendo 64. It was released exclusively in Japan in 1997 and licensed by J-League. The players have a cartoon appearance as opposed to other Japanese soccer games at the time, such as J-League Dynamite Soccer 64.
